## Here is a simpler version of the insructions from the README file:

1) Fork Repository to save it on Github account
2) Clone Repository like you usually would
3) Make sure VS Code, Python, and Git are all installed  
4) Set up virtual environemt 
    Use this command first: python -m venv venv (Says it works for mac, but I tried it and it works for windows too)
    Use this command second: pip install -r requirements.txt
5) Use this command:  uvicorn api.main:app --reload
6) Search this up on browser to see project: `http://127.0.0.1:8000 ***
7) Search this up on browser to see API documentation: http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs